OL,3,C'Traumatic' scheme left sexual assault
OL,4,Cvictim unable to sleep in own bed
OL,6,FA sexual assault victim says the
OL,7,Fsystem for claiming compensation in
OL,8,FJersey left her traumatised.
OL,10,FSpeaking exclusively to ITV News,
OL,11,FJenny said the process made her feel
OL,12,Fas though she was on trial.
OL,14,FThe Criminal Injuries Compensation
OL,15,FScheme reviews claims made by dozens
OL,16,Fof victims every year and can award
OL,17,Fthem up to #100,000.
OL,19,FJenny was raped in 2023 then, months
OL,20,Flater, was sexually assaulted by a
OL,21,Fdifferent man.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/8
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
