FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1780063875
OL,3,C'Traumatic' scheme left sexual assault
OL,4,Cvictim unable to sleep in own bed
OL,6,FHowever, her claim for compensation
OL,7,Ffollowing the sexual assault was
OL,8,Frejected.
OL,10,FJenny appealed the decision, and was
OL,11,Fbrought in for a hearing.
OL,13,FTalking about her experience, Jenny
OL,14,Fsaid: "I felt like it (the process)
OL,15,Fwas victim blaming. I'd already been
OL,16,Fthrough a trial, cross-examined for
OL,17,Ffour hours. I felt like they were
OL,18,Fcross-examining me again, and it was
OL,19,Ftraumatic."
OL,26,@vD@WpmvD@cpn
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/8
