OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1780063875
OL,3,C'Traumatic' scheme left sexual assault
OL,4,Cvictim unable to sleep in own bed
OL,6,FShe added: "They were implying that
OL,7,Fbecause I'd been raped before, why did
OL,8,FI allow a man in my house? Why did I
OL,9,Fallow myself to be vulnerable again?"
OL,11,FAnd after all this, Jenny's appeal was
OL,12,Frejected.
OL,14,FJenny said: "I wanted to pay for
OL,15,Fprivate rape counselling because I
OL,16,Fneed the help, I really need the help,
OL,17,Fbecause every single day it goes
OL,18,Fthrough my mind.
OL,20,F"I can't sleep in my bed."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/8
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
