FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1780063875
OL,3,C'Traumatic' scheme left sexual assault
OL,4,Cvictim unable to sleep in own bed
OL,6,FReflecting Jenny's call for change to
OL,7,Fthe system, Dr Deryn Evans, a forensic
OL,8,Fmedical examiner, said: "I've seen
OL,9,Fpeople whose teeth have been knocked
OL,10,Fout. It shouldn't be up to them to
OL,11,Fhave to pay.
OL,13,F"They're the victims."
OL,15,FAn independent review published in
OL,16,FFebruary looked into how Jersey's
OL,17,Fcriminal justice system deals with
OL,18,Fdomestic abuse, rape and sexual
OL,19,Fassault.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/8
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
