OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1780063875
OL,3,C'Traumatic' scheme left sexual assault
OL,4,Cvictim unable to sleep in own bed
OL,6,FIt identified three key complaints
OL,7,Fabout the Criminal Injuries
OL,8,FCompensation Scheme's board.
OL,10,FFirstly, it criticised rules which
OL,11,Fstate that all claims must be made
OL,12,Fwithin three years of an offence being
OL,13,Fcommitted.
OL,15,FSecondly, that it is up to victims to
OL,16,Fprovide, and pay for, medical evidence
OL,17,Fto prove they need compensation.
OL,19,FAnd finally, the tone of letters sent
OL,20,Fto victims was said to cause some of
OL,21,Fthem 'considerable stress'.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/8
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1780063875
OL,3,C'Traumatic' scheme left sexual assault
OL,4,Cvictim unable to sleep in own bed
OL,6,FThe report also recommended an
OL,7,Findependent review of the scheme,
OL,8,Fwhich has not been commissioned.
OL,10,FHowever, Jersey's government say this
OL,11,Fwill be considered in due course.
OL,13,FA spokesperson said that the
OL,14,FGovernment does "recognise the
OL,15,Fimportance of the compensation process
OL,16,Ffor victims of crime" and that there
OL,17,Fare "existing and well-established
OL,18,Flines of communication between it and
OL,19,Fvictims..."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G6/8
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1780063875
OL,3,C'Traumatic' scheme left sexual assault
OL,4,Cvictim unable to sleep in own bed
OL,6,FKate Wright, CEO of domestic abuse
OL,7,Fcharity Freeda, told ITV News that the
OL,8,Fproblem is broader and that wholesale
OL,9,Fchanges need to be made concerning the
OL,10,Fway victims of domestic abuse are
OL,11,Ftreated.
OL,13,F"You only have to speak to States of
OL,14,FJersey Police to hear how under
OL,15,Fpressure they are because demand is
OL,16,Fgoing up, and it's not just demand,
OL,17,Fit's complexity.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G7/8
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
