FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1780063875
OL,3,C'Traumatic' scheme left sexual assault
OL,4,Cvictim unable to sleep in own bed
OL,6,F"I'm sad to say, I think it's
OL,7,Fsymptomatic of the environment right
OL,8,Fnow but some of those more complex
OL,9,Fcases are becoming more violent so
OL,10,Finvestment in prevention is absolutely
OL,11,Fkey."
OL,13,FAs Jersey goes to the polls and with
OL,14,FSenators back on the ballot, ITV
OL,15,FChannel's Jess Dunsdon and Luke
OL,16,FKeohane break down the key election
OL,17,Fissues alongside expert guests. Listen
OL,18,Fto Jersey Votes wherever you get your
OL,19,Fpodcasts or watch on ITVX, and YouTube
OL,20,Fbelow, with new episodes each
OL,21,FThursday...
